DATA CLOUD
Salesforce-Enabled Large Language Models

Use a Salesforce-enabled foundation model to power your generative AI experiences with Prompt Builder. Some models use geo-aware request routing to accommodate data residency requirements. As a result, the provider can host their model in multiple regions while working within the boundaries of the Einstein Trust Layer.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on. To purchase the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on, contact your Salesforce account executive.

Edit a Salesforce-enabled model (standard configuration). You can then enter a test prompt, adjust one or more hyperparameters, and update the prompt settings based on the results you want to achieve.
